 Agency Opgroeien. You can find the contact details on the application form.</li></ul><p>The Agency will send you a confirmation of receipt no later than one month after receipt of the application. This is followed by an examination and possibly an adaptation period or an aptitude test. Within 4 months of the receipt of your complete application, the Agency will make a decision.</p><h3>You want to come to work temporarily in Flanders</h3><p>If you already work as a child care worker or supervisor in your country of origin and you want to work in Flanders temporarily, you have to send a written statement to the Agency Opgroeien. You can use the form <a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/raw/upload/v1643897408/verklaring-tijdelijke-en-incidentele-dienstverlening-formulier_wvexa5.docx\">‘verklaring tijdelijke en incidentele dienstverlening’ (statement of temporary and occasional services)</a> for this purpose. The form also lists the documents to be attached, such as proof of nationality and proof of your professional qualifications.</p><p>The Agency will send you a reply no later than one month after receipt of the form and documents. In some cases, you will still need to take an aptitude test.</p>"},"@type":"Procedure","order":0}],"websites":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Erkenning beroepskwalificaties kinderopvang","nl-BE-x-formal":"Erkenning beroepskwalificaties kinderopvang","en":"Erkenning beroepskwalificaties kinderopvang","nl":"Erkenning beroepskwalificaties kinderopvang"},"url":"https://www.kindengezin.be/sites/default/files/2021-05/erkenning-beroepskwalificaties-europa-procedure.pdf","@type":"Website","order":0}],"creatie":"2021-02-26T08:18:50Z","laatstGewijzigd":"2024-01-11T21:06:56Z","laatstOntvangen":"2024-01-30T16:11:00.569229791Z","productnummer":"1959","gearchiveerd":false,"publicatieLink":{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-formal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","en":"See also on vlaanderen.be","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Lees meer op vlaanderen.be","nl":"Lees